Acknowledgement The ALICE collaboration would like to thank
all its engineers and technicians for their invaluable contributions to
the construction of the experiment. We would like to thank and con-
gratulate the CERN accelerator teams for the outstanding performance
of the LHC complex at start up, and for providing us with the collisions
used for this paper on such a short notice!
